    <item>
      <title>欧盟组建团队以避免德拉吉发出“缓慢痛苦”的警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/eu-builds-team-to-avoid-draghi-s-warning-of-slow-agony-ahead</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌尔苏拉·冯德莱恩宣布了一项雄心勃勃的欧盟委员会重组计划，采纳了前欧洲央行行长马里奥·德拉吉的一些旨在增强欧盟竞争力的建议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/eu-builds-team-to-avoid-draghi-s-warning-of-slow-agony-ahead</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 15:07:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>惠誉称罗马尼亚面临债务激增风险，可能影响其评级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/romania-risks-debt-surge-that-could-impact-rating-fitch-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[惠誉评级分析师表示，罗马尼亚应迅速采取措施限制预算赤字的激增，该国预算赤字已成为欧盟中最大的国家，以避免失去投资级评级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/romania-risks-debt-surge-that-could-impact-rating-fitch-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 14:49:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>五角大楼修复发动机过热问题使 F-35 成本上涨 10% 至 4850 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/f-35-cost-rises-10-to-485-billion-to-fix-overheating-engines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于发动机改进所需的资金已被纳入美国最昂贵的武器系统的官方估算中，五角大楼开发和生产洛克希德马丁公司的 F-35 的成本已上涨近 10%，达到约 4850 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/f-35-cost-rises-10-to-485-billion-to-fix-overheating-engines</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 14:46:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>戴维的自由民主党利用新影响力推动工党，攻击英国保守党</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/davey-s-lib-dems-use-new-clout-to-nudge-labour-attack-uk-tories</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数周前，自由民主党在英国政坛重回第三的位置，而欣喜若狂的党魁埃德·戴维面临的问题是，他的中间派政党下一步该怎么做。周二，他在布莱顿举行的年度会议上发表讲话，传达的信息很明确：如果没有坏，就不要去修补。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/davey-s-lib-dems-use-new-clout-to-nudge-labour-attack-uk-tories</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 14:43:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黎巴嫩传呼机爆炸致数百人受伤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/pagers-in-lebanon-blast-including-hezbollah</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黎巴嫩当局称，周二在一次疑似袭击事件中，包括伊朗大使在内的数百人的传呼机发生爆炸，在全国各地受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/pagers-in-lebanon-blast-including-hezbollah</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 14:41:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>棕榈滩每天花费 93,000 美元保护特朗普后请求帮助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/palm-beach-asks-for-help-after-spending-93-000-a-day-to-protect-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[棕榈滩是美国最富有的地区之一，由于保护其最著名的居民——前总统唐纳德·特朗普——的费用飙升至每天 93,000 美元，该市正在寻求政府援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/palm-beach-asks-for-help-after-spending-93-000-a-day-to-protect-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 14:35:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储准备降息之际，巴西央行行长立场鹰派</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/brazil-braces-for-hawkish-central-bank-chief-just-as-fed-readies-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西央行新权力掮客加布里埃尔·加利波罗 (Gabriel Galipolo) 在过去几周内彻底转型为反通胀斗士。加利波罗被任命为央行行长，此举颠覆了拉丁美洲最大经济体的货币政策前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/brazil-braces-for-hawkish-central-bank-chief-just-as-fed-readies-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 11:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加纳主要反对派抗议要求审计选民名册</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/ghana-s-main-opposition-protests-to-demand-audit-of-voter-roll</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加纳最大的反对党于周二发起全国性抗议，要求在 12 月 7 日选举前对选民登记册进行法务审计。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/ghana-s-main-opposition-protests-to-demand-audit-of-voter-roll</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 09:32:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>葡萄牙消防员和飞机在阿威罗地区遭遇火灾</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/portuguese-firefighters-continue-to-face-blazes-in-aveiro-region</link>
      <description><![CDATA[过去两天气温升高，消防员继续在阿威罗地区和葡萄牙北部其他地区扑灭大火。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/portuguese-firefighters-continue-to-face-blazes-in-aveiro-region</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 08:16:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>蒙特利尔败选后特鲁多面临更大离职压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/trudeau-to-face-more-pressure-to-leave-after-montreal-defeat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多遭遇重大政治挫折，他领导的自由党在蒙特利尔一个选区的特别选举中落败，而直到最近，该选区还被认为是他的安全阵地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/trudeau-to-face-more-pressure-to-leave-after-montreal-defeat</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 07:08:13 GMT</pubDate>
